    "text": "Coming across <@U6KQ2S410>’s “thesis” earlier:\n\n<https://twitter.com/jonathoda/status/960952613507231744>\n\nHas made me reflect that, having come from a tech startup background before my PhD, when I stumbled into craft scholarship I leapt towards it because it was so alien to the “sensibilities” mentioned above! May have to cite this tweet now :slightly_smiling_face:",
